2.10	Tsidii_Le_Loka	Tsidii Le Loka	Tsidii Le Loka is an actress, vocalist, and composer originally from South Africa and The Kingdom of Lesotho. She is best known for creating the role of Rafiki in the original Broadway production of Disney's stage musical, The Lion King.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a4/Tsidii_Le_Loka.jpg/250px-Tsidii_Le_Loka.jpg
